net.canarymod.api

Interface Server

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CommandOwner, MessageReceiver, MOTDOwner, TaskOwner

    public interface Server
extends MessageReceiver, CommandOwner, TaskOwner, MOTDOwner
    CanaryMod Server.
    This handles communication to the server and provides a couple of useful information
    Author:
    Chris (damagefilter), Jason (darkdiplomat), Jos Kuijpers

      • getOfflinePlayer

        OfflinePlayer getOfflinePlayer(java.lang.String player)
        Get an OfflinePlayer. This will only return an OfflinePlayer instance if the playername resolves into a valid UUID via the Mojang API. if you try to get a player that never joined it will return an OfflinePlayer with the given name and default values
        Parameters:
        player - the name of the player
        Returns:
        the OfflinePlayer instance or null if the playername/uuid doesn't exist.
